1
00:00:01,306 --> 00:00:04,152
I want some envelopes, please.
请给我拿几个信封.

2
00:00:05,468 --> 00:00:09,110
Do you want the large size or the small size?
您要大号的还是小号的?

3
00:00:10,183 --> 00:00:12,407
The large size, please.
请拿大号的.

4
00:00:13,697 --> 00:00:16,396
Do you have any writing paper?
您有信纸吗?

5
00:00:17,418 --> 00:00:18,210
Yes, we do.
有.

6
00:00:19,355 --> 00:00:22,340
I don't have any small pads.
我没有小本的信纸,

7
00:00:23,152 --> 00:00:25,126
I only have large ones.
我只有大本的.

8
00:00:26,541 --> 00:00:28,271
Do you want a pad?
您要一本吗?

9
00:00:29,612 --> 00:00:30,564
Yes, please.
好, 请拿一本.

10
00:00:31,784 --> 00:00:33,908
And I want some glue.
我还要些胶水.

11
00:00:34,721 --> 00:00:36,099
A bottle of glue.
一瓶胶水.

12
00:00:37,209 --> 00:00:39,702
I only have small boxes.
我只有小盒的.

13
00:00:40,358 --> 00:00:41,534
Do you want one?
您要一盒吗?

14
00:00:42,415 --> 00:00:43,363
No, thank you.
不了, 谢谢你.

15
00:00:44,287 --> 00:00:45,114
Is that all?
就要这些吗?

16
00:00:46,168 --> 00:00:47,799
That's all, thank you.
就这些, 谢谢你.

17
00:00:48,628 --> 00:00:50,118
What else do you want?
您还要什么吗?

18
00:00:50,769 --> 00:00:53,129
I want my change.
我要找给我的零钱.

